ent-RMCJumpsuitFreelancer = форма наёмника-фрилансера
    .desc = Легко драпируемая полевая форма, идеальная для непринужденного наемника. Отдает порохом, яблочным пирогом, смазкой и следами сакэ.
ent-RMCJumpsuitFreelancerBluePants = mercenary's outfit
    .desc = A pair of tan camouflage pants coupled with a blue t-shirt. Commonly seen on mercenaries beholden to no nation, only their contracts.
ent-RMCJumpsuitFreelancerGreenPants = mercenary's outfit
    .desc = A pair of woodland green pants coupled with a white t-shirt. Commonly seen on mercenaries beholden to no nation, only their contracts.
ent-RMCJumpsuitFreelancerBlackPants = mercenary's outfit
    .desc = A pair of black tactical pants coupled with an olive t-shirt. Commonly seen on mercenaries beholden to no nation, only their contracts.
